   "source": [
    "# Maximum Covariance Analysis (MCA or SVD)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Parameter\n",
    "\n",
    "+ data1 and data2 (np.ndarray): shape (time, * space grid number)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Method\n",
    "\n",
    "+ solve: solve the SVD results \n",
    "\n",
    "+ get_pc(npt): get EC of first npt modes\n",
    "\n",
    "+ get_pt(npt): get spatial patterns of first npt modes\n",
    "\n",
    "+ get_eign: get eign values of SVD(MCA) result\n",
    "\n",
    "+ get_varperc: get the proportion of mode variance\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Example"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 0 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import sacpy as scp\n",
    "import xarray as xr\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import sacpy.Map\n",
    "import cartopy.crs as ccrs"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sst = scp.load_sst()['sst'].loc[\"1991\":\"2021\", -20:30, 150:275]\n",
    "ssta = scp.get_anom(sst)\n",
    "u = scp.load_10mwind()['u']\n",
    "v = scp.load_10mwind()['v']\n",
    "\n",
    "uua = scp.get_anom(u)\n",
    "vua = scp.get_anom(v)\n",
    "uv = np.concatenate([np.array(uua)[...,np.newaxis],np.array(vua)[...,np.newaxis]],axis=-1)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "svd = scp.SVD(ssta,uv,complex=False)\n",
    "svd.solve()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "ptl, ptr = svd.get_pt(3)\n",
    "pcl,pcr = svd.get_pc(3)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "upt ,vpt = ptr[...,0] , ptr[...,1]\n",
    "sst_pt = ptl"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 11,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [

      ]

     "execution_count": 11,

     "data": {

   "source": [
    "import cartopy.crs as ccrs\n",
    "import sacpy.Map\n",
    "lon , lat = np.array(ssta.lon) , np.array(ssta.lat)\n",
    "fig = plt.figure(figsize=[12,9])\n",
    "ax = fig.add_subplot(221,projection=ccrs.PlateCarree(central_longitude=180))\n",
    "m1 = ax.scontourf(lon,lat,sst_pt[0],cmap='RdBu_r',levels=np.linspace(-0.1,0.1,11),extend=\"both\")\n",
    "ax.scontour(m1,colors=\"black\")\n",
    "ax.squiver(lon,lat,upt[0],vpt[0])\n",
    "ax.init_map(smally=2.5)\n",
    "ax.set_title(\"Mode1\")\n",
    "ax2 = fig.add_subplot(222)\n",
    "ax2.plot(sst.time,pcl[0],label=\"left\")\n",
    "ax2.plot(sst.time,pcr[0],label=\"right\")\n",
    "ax2.legend()\n",
    "ax2.set_title(\"EC1\")\n",
    "ax3 = fig.add_subplot(223,projection=ccrs.PlateCarree(central_longitude=180))\n",
    "m2 = ax3.scontourf(lon,lat,sst_pt[1],cmap='RdBu_r',levels=np.linspace(-0.1,0.1,11),extend=\"both\")\n",
    "ax3.squiver(lon,lat,upt[1],vpt[1])\n",
    "ax3.scontour(m2,colors=\"black\")\n",
    "ax3.init_map(smally=2.5)\n",
    "ax3.set_title(\"Mode2\")\n",
    "ax4 = fig.add_subplot(224)\n",
    "ax4.plot(sst.time,pcl[1],label=\"left\")\n",
    "ax4.plot(sst.time,pcr[1],label=\"right\")\n",
    "ax4.legend()\n",
    "ax4.set_title(\"EC2\")\n",
    "cb_ax = fig.add_axes([0.1,0.06,0.4,0.02])\n",
    "fig.colorbar(m1,cax=cb_ax,orientation=\"horizontal\")"
   ]
  }
